 "id": 787400}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1583044904", "name": "windows", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1583044904", "title": "Windows", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows", "topics": 2092, "footer": "", "header": "Windows, not walls.", "title_alternative": "Windows", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1583044904", "stars": 698, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 360, "parent_node_name": "os"}, "member": {"username": "changwei", "website": "www.changwei.me", "github": "cw1997", "psn": "", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/196b/8221/119718_mini.png?m=1463287207", "bio": "QQ：867597730\r\nVX：changwei1006\r\n贴吧ID：昌维001\r\n喜欢做一些好玩的小项目，尝试一些新奇的东西。\r\n脑洞大开的二逼青年", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/changwei", "tagline": "達則兼濟天下，窮則獨善其身。", "twitter": "", "created": 1432989569, "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/196b/8221/119718_mini.png?m=1463287207", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/196b/8221/119718_mini.png?m=1463287207", "location": "臺灣 臺北市", "btc": "", "id": 119718}, "last_reply_by": "iamshang", "last_touched": 1625398916, "title": "Win10 下最好用的看图软件是？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/787453", "created": 1625386159, "content": "Win10 自带的相册太卡了，每次打开至少 1s 左右延迟(i5-9400 的配置在现在也不算过时吧)，切换图片的时候感觉也没有 Win7 的图片管理器那么快，以前 Win7 时代那个图片管理器真好啊，都是秒开，macOS 按空格速览这种交互方式也很快，Win10 下有没有什么比较快且好用的看图软件？", "content_rendered": "<p>Win10 自带的相册太卡了，每次打开至少 1s 左右延迟(i5-9400 的配置在现在也不算过时吧)，切换图片的时候感觉也没有 Win7 的图片管理器那么快，以前 Win7 时代那个图片管理器真好啊，都是秒开，macOS 按空格速览这种交互方式也很快，Win10 下有没有什么比较快且好用的看图软件？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1625388602, "replies": 20, "id": 787453}]